{"name":"Revelatory Glimpse","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages an ally, and both are within 15 feet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You interfere in the triggering attack and probe the enemy's tactics as you do so. The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to [[/r (2+@actor.level)]]{2 + your level}. Attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} about the enemy using Religion.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"revelatory-glimpse","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686465704775,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"0uqtTO0XW5j18oOI"}
{"name":"Devastating Strike","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You damage an enemy with a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You unleash a @Template[type:cone|distance:15] of devastation. It starts from the target of your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} and deals damage of your devastating energy equal to your level, with a @Check[type:reflex|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.spellDC.value)|traits:evocation|basic:true] save against your spell DC.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"devastating-strike","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion","evocation"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686465507792,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"1dcuRzj6eVLNAksc"}
{"name":"Lingering Suffering","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy within 15 feet succeeds at a flat check to end @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} or succeeds at a saving throw against an effect that deals damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You teach your foe the value of suffering.</p>\n<p>The triggering enemy must attempt the flat check or saving throw again and take the second result. They are then immune to your @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.actions.4Dml6z2N7VOKgQPI]{Lingering Suffering} for 1 hour.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"lingering-suffering","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion","misfortune"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":null,"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686465651442,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"4Dml6z2N7VOKgQPI"}
{"name":"Life Sap","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An enemy damages an ally, and both are within 15 feet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You intone tidings of the offender’s coming demise. The foe must choose one of the following options: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>The ally is unharmed by the triggering damage.</li>\n<li>The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to [[/r (2+@actor.level)]]{2 + your level}. After the damaging effect is applied, the enemy becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1}. The @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed} effect remains until the enemy spends an entire turn without harming the triggering ally.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"life-sap","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":null,"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464447914,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"7YmGwO79bcLHPCDH"}
{"name":"Impede Influence","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within 15 feet is affected by an emotion or mental effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You ward your ally’s mind and assail the attacker. The enemy who created the effect must choose one of the following options: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>The ally is unaffected by the triggering effect. </li>\n<li>The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering effect equal to [[/r 2+@actor.level]]{2 + your level}. After the effect is applied, the enemy becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 2} until the end of its next turn.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"impede-influence","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463782854,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"8ZZmNjjLI3qW7LDF"}
{"name":"Grim Honor","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy enters into flanking position, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strikes} while flanking, becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.zJxUflt9np0q4yML]{Invisible}, or uses a skill action that requires a Deception or Stealth check. The enemy must begin this action within your reach or move into your reach during this action.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You punish your foe for their impudent attempt at deception. Make a melee @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against the target, resolving the attack roll before they complete their action and gain its benefits. In addition to the usual effects on a hit, the triggering creature takes a -2 circumstance penalty on the check. On a critical hit, the penalty increases to -4.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> If you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.KAVf7AmRnbCAHrkT]{Attack of Opportunity}, you gain an additional reaction each round you can use for @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.actions.JH8BfWXO939neKtB]{Grim Honor}.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"grim-honor","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463617725,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"JH8BfWXO939neKtB"}
{"name":"Shrouded Strike","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You deal damage to an enemy within 15 feet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You retreat into cloying shadows. Attempt a Stealth check against the damaged enemy's Perception DC.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Hidden]{Hidden} to the damaged creature. Attempt another @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against the damaged creature. Your multiple attack penalty applies and increases as usual. You don't lose the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.iU0fEDdBp3rXpTMC]{Hidden} condition because of this @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> You become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.iU0fEDdBp3rXpTMC]{Hidden} to the damaged creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> You become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed} to the damaged creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> No effect.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"shrouded-strike","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"interaction","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464617945,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"LYc1W6RvCez8fmNT"}
{"name":"Glimpse of Pacifism","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages your ally, and both are within 15 feet of you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your foe hesitates as they consider the possibility of peace. The foe must choose one of the following options: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>The enemy must not deal any damage until the end of their next turn. If they do, they become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 2} for 1 round. </li>\n<li>The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to [[/r 2+@actor.level]]{2 + your level}. After the damaging effect is applied, the enemy becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 2} until the end of its next turn.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"glimpse-of-pacifism","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463853757,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"SPHb4DGVpRgSXYiD"}
{"name":"Allied Extension","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>Your ally within 15 feet succeeds but doesn’t critically succeed at an attack roll, and their target is within your reach.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You demonstrate the ways of perfection to your ally.</p>\n<p>Attempt a melee @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against your ally’s target. If you critically hit, your ally’s multiple attack penalty from the triggering @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} is reduced by 1.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"allied-extension","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464062265,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"TC1REEqTKDGXtySV"}
{"name":"Retributive Break","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An enemy attacks an ally with a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} but hasn’t made the attack roll yet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your enemy risks their weapon forsaking them. The enemy chooses to either lose the action or take a -2 item penalty with that weapon or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} until the end of their next turn, starting with the triggering @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}. This duration extends to 1 minute if the triggering @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} is a critical hit.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.effects.zw9PyJ9Sn0ajcPY0]{Effect: Retributive Break}</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"retributive-break","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":null,"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464856553,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"TPduAdK5uu0N3HnF"}
{"name":"Dervish Strike","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You or an ally critically hit an enemy and another enemy is within your reach.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You spin unexpectedly and attack the second enemy while their attention is distracted. Attempt a melee @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against the second enemy. They are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} against this @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"dervish-strike","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464658619,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"W1Z3yEJFypormLmt"}
{"name":"Retributive Tangle","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An enemy within 15 feet damages an ally.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You give the foe an opportunity to relent before invoking nature’s wrath. You cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.uZK2BYzPnxUBnDjr]{Tanglefoot} as a divine cantrip, targeting the triggering enemy. Before you make your spell attack roll, they can choose to forego the triggering damage to make the outcome one degree worse.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"retributive-tangle","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463968764,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"W9E6CRbddffxCoTD"}
{"name":"Ongoing Sting","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally damages an enemy within 15 feet, or an enemy within 15 feet ends @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} they are affected by.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You declare the creature’s suffering unfinished. The triggering enemy takes [[/r @actor.level[untyped,persistent]]]{persistent damage equal to your level} matching the triggering damage type. If there were multiple damage types, choose one. The creature then becomes immune to your @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.actions.XfvLaaqKigt1MGoX]{Ongoing Sting} for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"ongoing-sting","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463628733,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"XfvLaaqKigt1MGoX"}
{"name":"Defy Burden","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally takes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} (either initially or at the end of their turn) or gains a condition (other than @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.yZRUzMqrMmfLu0V1]{Dying} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Yl48xTdMh3aeQYL2]{Wounded}) with a numerical value.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You offer solace amidst turmoil. Your ally may attempt a flat check to end the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} or attempt a saving throw to reduce the condition’s numerical value by 1. If the condition resulted from a failed saving throw, use the same type of saving throw. If not, use:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fortitude</strong> for @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned};</li>\n<li><strong>Reflex </strong>for @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy};</li>\n<li><strong>Will </strong>for @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.3uh1r86TzbQvosxv]{Doomed}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied}.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"defy-burden","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463640917,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"aRGbSYdALsiPT1Vb"}
{"name":"Makeshift Shielding","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An ally within your reach takes damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You study the source of damage and begin cobbling together defenses against them. Choose one type of damage your ally has taken. They gain resistance to this damage equal to [[/r (2+@actor.level)]]{2 + your level} until the end of this combat. While this resistance lasts, you can spend an action with the manipulate trait to grant this same resistance to another ally within your reach with the same duration.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.effects.Bk6JNxZNqzh7eNd1]{Effect: Makeshift Shielding}</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"makeshift-shielding","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion","manipulate"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686465418215,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"d6dcmcSn8eoba0BX"}
{"name":"Retributive Aid","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your ally within 15 feet misses on a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You cover your ally with prayer.</p>\n<p>Attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.HCl3pzVefiv9ZKQW]{Aid} your ally with an attack roll or Religion skill check, possibly changing the outcome. Regardless, your ally gains resistance equal to [[/r 2+@actor.level]]{2 + your level} against all damage the next time they take damage before the start of their next turn.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"retributive-aid","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464072703,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"gEo2or7xSvDEhejW"}
{"name":"Aiding Strike","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>An ally attempts a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against an enemy within your reach.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You join your blade in harmony with your ally’s attack. Attempt a melee @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} against the enemy. On a hit, you also succeed at @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.HCl3pzVefiv9ZKQW]{Aiding} your ally’s attack roll, and you critically succeed if your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} was a critical hit.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"aiding-strike","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686463917861,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"lHM2DGmAgnqfaLqm"}
{"name":"Balanced Aid","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within 30 feet damages an enemy or heals a creature.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You balance the energies of the battlefield. If your triggering ally damaged an enemy, you grant [[/r (2+@actor.level)]]{2 + your level} temporary Hit Points to an ally within 30 feet. They last until the next time you use @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.actions.mmm1Qj11uSEgHIcA]{Balanced Aid}, up to a maximum of 1 minute.</p>\n<p>If your ally healed a creature, you deal force damage equal to [[/r (2+@actor.level)[force]]]{2 + your level} to an enemy within 30 feet.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"balanced-aid","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"interaction","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464288645,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"mmm1Qj11uSEgHIcA"}
{"name":"Boundless Destruction","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You damage an enemy within 15 feet and they are not reduced to 0 Hit Points.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You issue forth a torrent of destruction that seems to never end. The damaged creature chooses one of the following. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>The damaged creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1}.</li>\n<li>The damaged creature takes persistent damage of the same type [[/r (@actor.level)[persistent]]]{equal to your level}. If this reaction was triggered by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{Persistent Damage} you caused, you instead deal additional damage once equal to [[/r ceil((@actor.level)/2)]]{half your level rounded up}.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"boundless-destruction","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464626609,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"nEllkRP44zBjfo5c"}
{"name":"Retributive Disarm","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages your ally, and both are within 15 feet of you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You protect your ally and strike your foe. The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to [[/r 2+@actor.level]]{2 + your level}. If the foe is within reach, attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Dt6B1slsBy8ipJu9]{Disarm} it. You don’t need a free hand to do so.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"retributive-disarm","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464663935,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"nOjg973NIJgfi6b9"}
{"name":"Judge","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>You scrutinize a creature and compare their actions against the precepts of your faith. Select yourself or a conscious creature you can see, and choose condemnation or plaudit. The creature becomes your claimant. You can have one @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.effects.xg3c12QeyDmDQHG9]{Claimant} at a time, and the designation lasts until they fall unconscious, until you use Judge again and replace them with another claimant, or until 1 minute passes. At 12th level, you can have up to two claimants. You can select two claimants when you Judge, or you can select a second claimant on a subsequent use of Judge. At 20th level, you can have up to three claimants. You can select three claimants when you Judge, or a second and third claimant on subsequent uses of Judge. If you use Judge when you have your maximum number of claimants, you choose which claimants to replace.</p>\n<p>If you choose @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.effects.Z0LmG4Alp1UUic9z]{Condemnation} for a claimant, your @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strikes} and spells deal 1 additional damage to this claimant. You can use condemnation judgments that this claimant triggers, and you can cast condemnation sentence cantrips against them. The additional damage increases by 1 each time you use a condemnation judgment against them, up to a maximum of your spellcasting ability modifier.</p>\n<p>If you choose @UUID[Compendium.divine-causes-and-inquisitions.effects.6XeALgiMxcq3AFWs]{Plaudit} for a claimant, the claimant gains temporary Hit Points equal to 2 + half your level that last until the end of your next turn. This is a healing effect. You can use plaudit judgments that this claimant triggers and can cast plaudit sentence cantrips against them.</p>\n<p>Although it’s likely rare, you can, as a free action, switch between condemnation and plaudit for a claimant.</p>\n<p>You might, for example, switch from plaudit to condemnation if an ally becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.9qGBRpbX9NEwtAAr]{Controlled}, or you might switch from condemnation to plaudit if an enemy loses the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.9qGBRpbX9NEwtAAr]{Controlled} condition and begins fighting alongside you.</p>\n<p> </p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"rules":[],"slug":"judge","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","hb_inquisitor"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"offensive","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"round"}},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.d46Xaw1IM7lO9cJg"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686353350268,"modifiedTime":1686358409830,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"q4HzZswft1Hu11sC"}
{"name":"Retributive Grasp","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy within 15 feet damages you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You capture your enemy’s attention.</p>\n<p>The foe must choose one of the following options. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>You take no damage, and the enemy loses the action.</li>\n<li>You gain resistance equal to [[/r 2+@actor.level]]{2 + your level} against all triggering damage. The enemy becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.AdPVz7rbaVSRxHFg]{Fascinated} by you.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":"retributive-grasp","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["champion"]},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"category":"defensive","actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1686382850523,"modifiedTime":1686464149915,"lastModifiedBy":"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Ug3CFCbSz7POT3UI":3},"_id":"w5i0DmB2fwmK02Ke"}
